PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD REGULATIONS by replacing an incorrect cross-reference to the Act found in section 29, and by broadening the definition of "other grades" of amber durum wheat so that it covers all other grades, instead of just the off grades, effective August 1, 2001.

precis:
Regulations Amending the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD REGULATIONS by replacing an
incorrect cross-reference to the Act found in section 29, and by broadening
the definition of "other grades" of amber durum wheat so that it covers all
other grades, instead of just the off grades, effective August 1, 2001.
